Pin down version range of pandas

Install as-dataframe not requirements.txt

Install the package as-dataframe which will also install pandas. We do
not need to install from requirements.txt anymore.

Do not import as_dataframe

Do not import as_dataframe to get the version because importing it
requires that pandas is installed, and pandas gets installed only during
the installation. We could probably install pandas by specifying it in
`setup_requires` but I am not sure this is Pythonic so to say.
